<br>
Lavastorm<br>
   Our ward line is useful here.  There are decent drops if you are not twinked (I was not) and you can sell right in the zone when you get too much loot.<br>
<br>
Oasis<br>
    I know. Tons of folks, but doing caimens and crocs really is some great xp.  <br>
<br>
Unrest<br>
    I did the yard trash for a few levels.  For the most part the zone is empty now (/rude Kunark) and you can just solo the yard trash.  Loot is not bad and the mushroom drops are 3-4gp each and stack.  So it adds up.<br>
<br>
Steamfont<br>
    Ok, I move around a bunch.. sue me <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Outside of the Mino caves all the stuff is blue and decent xp.  Loot is not great, but I like Steamfont, since nobody hunts there.<br>
<br>
